title: 1 Bedroom, Lower Level with Walkout Patio & Pet Friendly
posting_body: ['1 Bedroom , 1 Bath, Lower Level with Walkout Patio and Pet Friendly', 'Our homes features gourmet kitchens with granite counter tops, center islands, stainless steel appliances, dishwashers and microwaves.', ' This unit has 1 bedroom, 1 bath, full-size washer & dryer in unit and private door to the attached garage.', 'Enjoy your walk-in closets, private patio and central air conditioning.', 'Enjoy some of the added luxuries including: indoor and outdoor pools, basketball & tennis courts, exercise facility, party room (to rent) and a private off leash dog run.', 'Located close to Shady Oak Beach on the border of Hopkins/Minnetonka and only ten minutes from downtown Minneapolis.', 'Please call', 'show contact info', 'to set up a self-guided tour.', '993 Woodhill Court, Hopkins, MN 55343', 'Mon - Fri: 9:00 am - 5:00 pm', 'Saturday:', 'By Appointment', 'Sunday: Closed', 'Professionally Managed by StuartCo', 'CONTACT US FOR MORE DETAILS', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Facebook:  <URL>', 'Website:  <URL>', '-COPY/PASTE OUR WEBSITE INTO YOUR BROWSER FOR MORE INFO', '****Security deposit$350, application fees $50 per adult due at the time of application.', 'Move-in fee $200 are due at time of approval.', '*', '**', 'Community Features', '24 Hour Fitness Center', 'Party Room With Full Kitchen', 'Outdoor and Indoor Pool', 'Basketball and Tennis Court', 'Playground', 'Access to Shady Oak Beach', 'Fenced Pet Park', 'Access to Walking/Biking/Jogging Trail', 'On Site Maintenance & Management', 'Apartment Features', 'Gourmet Kitchens with Center Islands', 'Private Entrance', 'Private Balcony or Raised Deck', 'Fully Equipped Appliances', 'Attached Garage', 'Abundant Closet Space', 'Intrusion Alarm System']
